## 🚀 What can the program do?

### 1. Read Text (OCR)
- Upload any image with text
- The program processes it (turns it to black and white, removes noise)
- It extracts the text and shows it to you
- Shows confidence score (how sure it is)

### 2. Detect Objects
- Upload an image with objects (people, cars, animals)
- The program draws green boxes around detected objects
- Shows confidence percentage for each object

### 3. Both Together
- You can run both recognition types at the same time
- See text extraction AND object detection in one go

---

## 📊 The 80% Gate Explained
if confidence is greater than or equal to 80 percent:
ACCEPT - Show the result
else:
REJECT - Ignore it (prevents wrong guesses)

text

**Why 80%?** 
- The AI doesn't "know" - it just calculates probabilities
- 80% ensures high accuracy with few false positives
- Prevents the AI from "hallucinating" (seeing things that aren't there)

