## 🖥️ How to Use the App

### Step-by-Step:

1. **Open the app** in your browser

2. **Choose an image source** from the sidebar:
   - 📁 From Images Folder (use images you saved in the images folder)
   - 📤 Upload Image (upload any picture from your computer)
   - 🎨 Sample Image (use the built-in test image)

3. **Choose what you want to recognize**:
   - 📝 Text Recognition only
   - 🎯 Object Detection only
   - 🤖 Both (do everything)

4. **Adjust settings** (optional):
   - PSM Mode: How the OCR reads text (Automatic works best)
   - Confidence Threshold: Set the minimum confidence (80% default)

5. **View results**:
   - Extracted text appears in a box
   - Confidence score shows how sure the AI is
   - Green boxes highlight detected text or objects

6. **Download results** (optional):
   - Click "Download Text" to save extracted text as a file

