## 🐛 Common Problems and Solutions

| Problem | Solution |
|---------|----------|
| "No module named 'pytesseract'" | Run: pip install pytesseract |
| "Tesseract not found" | Check Tesseract is installed and path is correct |
| "No images in folder" | Create images folder and add pictures |
| "Low confidence (below 80%)" | Use clearer images with better lighting |
| "App won't start" | Make sure you ran streamlit run app.py |

